вҹҰ Test Unicode operators in typechecker вҹ§

e console

О»main()вҶ’рқ•Ң=console.log("All tests passed: " ++ test_le(5,10) ++ ", " ++ test_ge(10,5) ++ ", " ++ test_ne(5,10) ++ ", " ++ В¬test_and(true,false) ++ ", " ++ test_or(true,false))

вҹҰ Test and / or вҹ§
